      Hi, I'm **Kamil Kowalski**. I'm a software developer specializing in web applications.
      I've been working in the web industry **since 2008**, started with PHP apps based on open-source
      frameworks like WordPress, Joomla! and Typo3, gradually moving to MVC frameworks like **Zend and CakePHP**,
      and finally arriving at my now-language-of-choice: **Ruby**.

      The biggest projects I've been working on are [WebOrg](http://www.weborg.no/) and
      [SBS Discovery Pressweb](http://presse.sbsdiscovery.no/), as well as a host of smaller websites and components.
      I'm experienced in **Rails**, integrating with **Amazon Web Services**, creating **APIs**, **testing and CI**,
      deployment, optimizing, application monitoring, and version control.

